    "namespace": "DE\\RUB\\StopwatchExternalModule",
    
    "description": "A REDCap External Module that provides a stopwatch widget that can be integrated into data entry forms or surveys. Results (elapsed time, times started/stopped) can be captured in a number of ways. For more details and to report bugs, please see this module's <a href=\"https://github.com/davwillev/stopwatch\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a> page.",
